{
  "stem": "17515.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 446.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the Polish people, I don't know how they organize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The inside, outside, are-- drive motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not but-- not everybody-- not-- not everybody allowed to-- to leave camp, staying there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Polish people guarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because many German kapos, we-- we keep them in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- so that's why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe one week.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody went on their free-- free-- on their free-- we went by group, 15 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So went to Linz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About-- not far away from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that time the SS prisoner run away also, from forest, from all different direction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the SS attack us too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They shoot us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- we-- we-- could get the military hardware.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had about a dozen German woman to cook for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were very organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And plenty people died because they was weak in the stomach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they ate too much and couldn't--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a month.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then after the American Army took us to the army trucks and brought us to the-- that'd be Regensburg, close to Regensburg, Hohenfels.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's a German town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe South-- South Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was still sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still have my [INAUDIBLE] on the leg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I wound up six months in a US hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Almost, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I leave hospital.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe after that I came to Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hear they organize the Polish-- US Army organize the Polish people to join them to the US Army as to be security guard for the US Army, for the-- for the top brass, to watch the Motor Pool, Air Force, air-- airport and for-- for the warehouses.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was And some hotels, which the brass is staying there, that we'd been watching.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, long.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A couple years.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
